---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Services | AI‑Native.es"
  description="Senior product, growth, and creative services for teams in Spain who want international‑grade execution."
>
  <section class="px-6 pb-20 pt-16 md:pt-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl text-center" data-animation="fade-up">
      <h1 class="mb-4 text-3xl font-bold md:text-5xl">Services</h1>
      <p class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-zinc-400">
        We are a small, senior team. Every project is led by our core partners and backed by an international crew across
        UX, CRO, SEA, and content. Below is how we typically plug into teams in Spain and across Europe.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto mt-16 grid max-w-6xl gap-8 md:grid-cols-2" data-animation="fade-up">
      <a
        href="/services/user-interface-user-research"
        class="group rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/60 p-8 transition-colors hover:border-cyan-400/60"
      >
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-cyan-300">
          Product foundations
        </h2>
        <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold">User interface & user research</h3>
        <p class="mb-4 text-sm text-zinc-400">
          From discovery to high‑fidelity UI, we help you ship products that feel obvious to use – and measurable in
          their impact.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500">
          Led by our product design and research leadership with experience at high‑volume European platforms.
        </p>
      </a>

      <a
        href="/services/european-accessibility-compliance"
        class="group rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/60 p-8 transition-colors hover:border-cyan-400/60"
      >
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-cyan-300">
          Compliance & inclusion
        </h2>
        <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold">European accessibility compliance</h3>
        <p class="mb-4 text-sm text-zinc-400">
          Practical WCAG and European Accessibility Act readiness for Spanish organisations who need clarity, not
          200‑page PDFs.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500">
          Audits, prioritised roadmaps, and training so your team can continue improving after we leave.
        </p>
      </a>

      <a
        href="/services/european-pricing-compliance"
        class="group rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/60 p-8 transition-colors hover:border-cyan-400/60"
      >
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-cyan-300">
          Legal‑ready UX
        </h2>
        <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold">EU Omnibus & pricing compliance</h3>
        <p class="mb-4 text-sm text-zinc-400">
          We redesign your pricing experience to align with the EU Price Indication Directive while keeping it
          conversion‑friendly.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500">
          Clear rules for discounts, strikethrough prices, and promotions that reduce legal risk instead of creating it.
        </p>
      </a>

      <a
        href="/services/conversion-optimization"
        class="group rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/60 p-8 transition-colors hover:border-cyan-400/60"
      >
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-cyan-300">
          Growth programs
        </h2>
        <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold">Conversion optimisation (CRO)</h3>
        <p class="mb-4 text-sm text-zinc-400">
          Structured experimentation programs, A/B tests, and UX improvements tied directly to revenue, margin, and
          customer lifetime value.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500">
          Designed for teams who want to grow profitably – not just “more traffic”.
        </p>
      </a>

      <a
        href="/services/sea-performance-marketing"
        class="group rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/60 p-8 transition-colors hover:border-cyan-400/60"
      >
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-cyan-300">
          Paid growth
        </h2>
        <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold">SEA & performance marketing</h3>
        <p class="mb-4 text-sm text-zinc-400">
          Deep audits and rebuilds of your Google Ads and performance setup, with a clear link to business outcomes –
          not vanity metrics.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500">
          Led by our growth and acquisition team, combining SEA, SEO, and analytics for one combined growth picture.
        </p>
      </a>

      <a
        href="/services/digital-photoshoots-video"
        class="group rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/60 p-8 transition-colors hover:border-cyan-400/60"
      >
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-cyan-300">
          Content & production
        </h2>
        <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold">Digital photoshoots & video generation</h3>
        <p class="mb-4 text-sm text-zinc-400">
          Creative direction, photography, and motion content that actually fits your product strategy and brand – not
          stock templates.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500">
          We work with a trusted network of photographers, directors, and AI tools to keep production fast and lean.
        </p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

